Simulating beamshape and UV-coverage using CASA and a simms generated ANTENNA table.

Input assumed
-----
 - MeerKAT subarray layout

Requires
-----
[casapy](http://casa.nrao.edu/casa_obtaining.shtml)
[pyxis](https://github.com/SpheMakh/pyxis)
makems and simms from [radio-astro](https://launchpad.net/~radio-astro/+archive/ubuntu/main)

Usage
-----
mkat_config.py -- contains MeerKAT array configuration and hardcoded array values
make_simms_setup.py -- autogen .cfg file used by simms
make_cfg.py -- generate measurement set to get ANTENNA table for configuration

Subarray layout scripts
-----
https://github.com/ska-sa/katsdpresearch/tree/ar2-psf

